.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Transport: quad-bike, bike, car, ship, trike
Hobby: singing, fishing, baking, dancing, board-games
City: london, new-york, marseilles, berlin, hamburg
Game: quad-bikemaster, go, domino, whist, bridge
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Hobby:singing == Transport:car
2. Hobby:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Hobby:fishing == City:berlin
4. Transport:bike is on the left of Transport:ship
5. Transport:bike == City:new-york
6. Game:domino == Pet:bird
7. Transport:trike == Game:go
8. City:marseilles is in the middle
9. Hobby:dancing is on the far left
10. Game:bridge is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Game:go
12. Game:quad-bikemaster == City:london
13. Hobby:baking == Game:whist
14. Hobby:dancing is on the left or right of Transport:quad-bike
15. Game:bridge is on the left or right of City:hamburg

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Transport		|    trike	|     quad-bike	|      car	|     bike	|     ship	|
| Hobby	|   dancing	|    fishing	|    singing	|    baking	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| City	|    hamburg	|     berlin	|     marseilles	|    new-york	|      london	|
| Game		|   go	|    bridge	|  domino	|    whist	|   quad-bikemaster	|
